<div class='intro'>
<span class='welcome'>Welcome to <span class='welcomeTravel'>Travel</span><span class='welcomeSage'>Sage</span> –</span> A guide that allows adventurous people to draw the curtain to the most exciting cities in the world.  As insanely-passionate travelers, we're here to help you customize your 

authentic experience.
<br>
<span class='callToAction'>Have an authentic experience to share?</span>  Click <%= link_to "here", "#", class: "submitContent" %> to upload your tale as one of our Travelers.
</div>

<div class='filterDiv'>To start, choose a feature article below – or – click <%=link_to "here", "#", class: "filterButton"%> to filter based upon your preferences:</div>
<%= render 'filter' %>
<div class='articlesDiv'>
  <% @cities.each do |city|%>
  <%= link_to city_path(city), class: "cityLink"  do %>
    <%= city.name %>, <%= city.province %>
    <% end %>
      <%city.articles.each do |article|  %>
        <div class='singleArticle'>
          <div class='articleText'>
            <span class='articleTitle'><%=link_to article.title, article_path(article)%></span><br>
            <span class='articleAuthor'>By: <%=link_to article.user.username, user_path(article.user) %></span>
          </div>
          <span class='articleTags'>
            <% article.categories.each do |tag| %>
              <%= link_to tag.name, category_path(tag) %>|
            <% end %>
          </span>
        </div>
      <% end %>
  <% end %>
</div>
